node.text: The new album is named for West’s late mother, who passed away in 2007. While DONDA explores a wider range of genres than his previous album Jesus is King, it features some of the religious themes that West has pivoted to in his recent music. A partial tracklist posted by West ahead of the release listed titles like “Pure Souls” and “Keep My Spirit Alive.” The album will be available for purchase and streaming on July 23rd.

node.text: Founded by Jeff Bezos, space travel company Blue Origin completed its first passenger flight on July 20. The rocket, named New Shepard, carried Bezos and three other passengers more than 65-miles above Earth, just to the boundary of space, known as the Kármán line. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to learn more.

node.title: @jeffbezos Completes His First Flight into Space

node.text:
The next @apple Watch is experiencing delays with several reports indicating  manufacturing and production issues. Recently, it was revealed that the Apple Watch 7 would include flatter sides and larger displays, an upgrade that makes the newest smartwatch have a more complex design. @hypebeastwatches: @urwerkgeneve has created a 25-piece limited edition run of its UR-100 of Electrum, an alloy that was used to make the earliest coins. Electrum is a naturally occurring mixture of gold, silver, and other metals found in the wild, URWERK produced a 2N 18k yellow gold alloy of gold and palladium to replicate its vivid “sunny” tone. The UR-100 indicates the time using a rotating carousel of three “wandering hour” satellites which track against a minute scale one after the other. The price is set at approximately $67,700 USD.⁠⁠
Photo: URWERK
